Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.18,0:31:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,あっうわー
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.94,0:31:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,ハハハ...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.65,0:31:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,よいしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.69,0:31:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,斜めってる！アハハハ
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.69,0:31:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ハァハァ...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.11,0:31:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,あ！アリさんこんにちは
