Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.34,0:34:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF0CFA7&}（花）{\c&HDEDEDE&}あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.03,0:34:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,わあっ！
