Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.77,0:57:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,ハァハァ
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.81,0:57:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,雨...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.86,0:57:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,雨！
